darks.orm.annotation.sqlmap
注释类型 Select

@Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Select

Indicates the SqlMap query method which is used to query SqlMap object list, single object or page object.

Query.java

从以下版本开始：
JDK1.5
版本：
1.0.0 v05/01/2012
作者：
Liu LiHua

必需元素摘要
 java.lang.Class<?> resultType
          query result type.Required.
 
可选元素摘要
 java.lang.String alias
          The alias string used in cascade query
 java.lang.String attribute
          The attributes string used in cascade query
 boolean autoCache
          If true, It will automatically use the global cache, if the global cache is enabled in the configuration file.If not, It need to manually configure the caching in the group cache id.
 boolean autoCascade
          if true, At query time automatically to the entity class injection with information related to the foreign key entity object.However, more complex cascade queries cannot correct injection.If not, The need to manually configure cascade query information, it can handle more complex cascade of query
 java.lang.String cacheId
          Cache id which is configured in the cache group of configuration file
 java.lang.String page
          The values string for select and constitude
 java.lang.String pageSize
          The values string for select and constitude
 Select.QueryType queryType
          Query result type.Required.
 java.lang.String SQL
          SQL query sentence.Required.
 java.lang.String values
          The values string for select and constitude

autoCache

public abstract boolean autoCache
If true, It will automatically use the global cache, if the global cache is enabled in the configuration file.If not, It need to manually configure the caching in the group cache id.

默认值：
true

autoCascade

public abstract boolean autoCascade
if true, At query time automatically to the entity class injection with information related to the foreign key entity object.However, more complex cascade queries cannot correct injection.If not, The need to manually configure cascade query information, it can handle more complex cascade of query

默认值：
true
